Package dsiter.row

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IColumnAccessor
    An extension of IRowAccessor for implementations that simply access a Column within a Row and return that value.
    IColumnAccessor.BOOLEAN
    An IColumnAccessor that is also an IRowAccessor.BOOLEAN
    IColumnAccessor.DOUBLE
    An IColumnAccessor that is also an IRowAccessor.DOUBLE
    IColumnAccessor.FLOAT
    An IColumnAccessor that is also an IRowAccessor.FLOAT
    IColumnAccessor.INT
    An IColumnAccessor that is also an IRowAccessor.INT
    IColumnAccessor.JSDATE
    An IColumnAccessor that is also an IRowAccessor.JSDATE
    IColumnAccessor.LONG
    An IColumnAccessor that is also an IRowAccessor.LONG
    IColumnAccessor.STRING
    An IColumnAccessor that is also an IRowAccessor.STRING
    IParserMutator
    Interface for classes that parse strings and insert them directly into Rows.
    IRowAccessor
    An interface representing objects that return values from Rows.
    IRowAccessor.BOOLEAN
    An IRowAccessor that returns a value of type boolean (i.e. getType() == ColumnType.BOOLEAN).
    IRowAccessor.DOUBLE
    An IRowAccessor that returns a value of type double (i.e. getType() == ColumnType.DOUBLE).
    IRowAccessor.FLOAT
    An IRowAccessor that returns a value of type float (i.e. getType() == ColumnType.FLOAT).
    IRowAccessor.INT
    An IRowAccessor that returns a value of type int (i.e. getType() == ColumnType.INT).
    IRowAccessor.JSDATE
    An IRowAccessor that returns a value of type long (i.e. getType() == ColumnType.JSDATE).
    IRowAccessor.LONG
    An IRowAccessor that returns a value of type long (i.e. getType() == ColumnType.LONG).
    IRowAccessor.STRING
    An IRowAccessor that returns a value of type String (i.e. getType() == ColumnType.STRING).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColumnDescriptor
    Class that describes a Column from a dataset.
    Row
    A Row represents a piece of data returned from an IDataset.
    RowCopier
    Class that manages copying data from one Row to another.
    RowShape
    Class that describes the "shape" of a Row.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ColumnType
    Enum that lists the various "primitive" types supported by Row
